      • updateTable

        public void updateTable(User user,
                        boolean execOrNot)
        This method updates the tables by clearing all data, making a call to dbm to get list of executables. This methods adds the new data to the table to display the most current.
        Parameters:
        user - This is User type that we build the table from.
        execOrNot - This is a boolean that decides which table to build.
